    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Philosophy & Approach</h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-section-primary">Coherence Over Chaos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Every system I build is designed with a unified purpose. Not rigid uniformity,
              but organic harmony where each component serves the whole. From code architecture
              to system design to musical composition ‚Äî coherence is the guiding principle.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-section-secondary">First Principles Thinking</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              I approach problems by decomposing them to their fundamental components.
              Understanding the deep structure of a system enables building solutions that
              are elegant, scalable, and resilient.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-section-primary">Building for Emergence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              The most interesting properties of systems aren't programmed ‚Äî they emerge
              from the interactions of simpler components. I design systems that create
              the conditions for intelligence to arise naturally.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Journey -->
